 war', certainly but only those Americans visited war. At the personal level YOU (ordinary WW2 America) were still at home, across the Atlantic, there was no military action fought upon America and civilian order remained pretty stable. (Aside from Pearl Harbor, a Japanese attack)<br><br>Newsflash, I'm not British nor European nor American. Your irrelevance is astonishing. I find the implied nationality a dumb conclusion since I never offered that inference.<br><br>As for my opinion, I still believe America did military service but bear in mind I do not believe you entirely suffered the true cost met by Europe for that war. Boasts will not alter a perception of that view with raucous hype. <br><br>I choose to regard that war with horror not envy. <br><br>Misty   <p><img src="http://users.bigpond.com/dwmac/eqme3.jpg"></h1></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showMessageRange?topicID=258.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showMessageRange?topicID=258.topic&start=41&stop=48>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showPrevMessage?topicID=258.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showNextMessage?topicID=258.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=258.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.emailToFriend?topicID=258.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.threadControl?topicID=258.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgf